query:
UPDATE "EmailInsightsBackfillBatch"
        SET 
            status = $2::"insights_backfill_batch_status",
            "errorMessage" = $3,
            "sqsMessageId" = COALESCE("sqsMessageId", $4),
            "startedAt" = COALESCE("startedAt", $5),
            "completedAt" = $6,
            "updatedAt" = $7
        WHERE id = $1
